{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x42,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I knew I'd find you if I waited here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Thank you so much for the other day. I've been studying hard, using that book as a reference."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "There's no need to thank me. Putting it to proper use is entirely up to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Besides, I'm not here to talk about that. I was thinking it's about time..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Let's go somewhere we can talk.<CR>This is going to take a while."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "You have a workshop in this town as well, correct?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yes, but it's a bit messy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I don't mind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...an alchemy cauldron. Your method is quite old-fashioned, though it does have a certain charm."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's the same medicine cauldron I've always used. Stirring cauldrons helps me relax..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I can't agree or sympathize with that, but it's your personal preference, so I would have to assume it's true."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "However, such a simple bookshelf... It seems you have unique books on medicine, but your collection is still meager."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Does your knowledge come from an oral tradition?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Half of it came from books, and the other half was taught to me by my grandfather himself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "So, the skill was fully passed down from one generation to another..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "No. My grandfather passed away before he was able to teach me everything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "The amount of the ingredients or the ratio of the mixtures are pretty much guesses. Hehehe..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "But I'm pretty confident that I kinda know what makes it work or fail..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x4e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I see, guesses and kindas...<CR>Hmhmhmhm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* You're laughing at me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "No, I beg your pardon. I apologize if I made you feel bad, but I didn't mean to look down on you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "However, this workshop is severely lacking. Let me give you this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Wow, I can really have this? Wait...I feel like I've seen this before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I'm not surprised that you recognize it. It's from the village where all those people disappeared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "That's right! You took it away from me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I still won't tell you what this vessel is. However, don't move it from here, or it won't be useful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Now, sorry to keep you waiting, but let's move on to the main subject."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Yes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I have a job for you. I want you to use your alchemy to make me an item."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Use...my alchemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "That's right. It can be anything.<CR>The medicine you specialize in making,<CR>or a rare metal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "However, you are restricted to creating something under the assumption that I will be using it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Ehh, you will...? Th-That's a bit..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Would you really be satisfied with an item that I make...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "The point of the request is to see if that's possible or not."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? Wh-What do you mean...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cc,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Before I tell you that...let me tell you an old story."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "No one knows about it in this area, but where I'm from, a few decades ago..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy was \"rediscovered,\" due to a certain incident."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1ce,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Many people put their hearts and souls into mastering their skills...and I was one of them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "To us, alchemy was \"possibility\" itself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "My colleagues and I were elated with the excellence of alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "However, one day, I came to realize that no single person truly understood alchemy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "That everyone was a sham alchemist,<CR>who had only scratched the surface<CR>of the art."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Sham...alchemists..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "Satisfied with showing off their insubstantial knowledge, some never bothered to pursue the truth..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "Others refused to even try to understand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "Even if you simply imitate the form, you can use the skill to a certain extent."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1d0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "msg_string": "However, the things they created were nothing but shams."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "msg_string": "To me, that was unforgivable. Alchemy books, equipment, facilities...I destroyed everything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "msg_string": "Because of that, I have become a man on the run. Though, I don't regret anything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x34,
            "msg_string": "I understand your story, and what you're trying to say..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x35,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Depending on the matter and nature of what you create, I may...take alchemy away from you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x36,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy should only be handled by those worthy of it. It's sacrilege for someone without ability to pursue it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x37,
            "msg_string": "I can understand that synthesizing with only partial knowledge of what you're doing is dangerous..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x38,
            "msg_string": "But to save my sister, to save Nio...I need alchemy... You taught me that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x39,
            "msg_string": "So, why?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3a,
            "msg_string": "This and that are different problems."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3b,
            "msg_string": "Hey now! Why are you assuming that you'll fail from the beginning? You just need to convince me that you're worthy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3c,
            "msg_string": "I won't set a specific deadline. When you finish something that you think is right for this, bring it to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3d,
            "msg_string": "I'll prepare a generous reward, as well. That's all I came to say."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3e,
            "msg_string": "(Wh-What should I do?<CR>This is really major...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3f,
            "msg_string": "(I might be forced to stop doing<CR>alchemy...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x40,
            "msg_string": "(I just have to make something super,<CR>and make sure Mr. Keith approves of<CR>me...!)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc8,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x41,
            "msg_string": "(*sigh* I wonder if I can do that...)"
        }
    ]
}